{"_attachments":{},"_id":"hexo-front-matter","_rev":"288382-61f1c4362c1293059b20e83a","author":{"name":"Tommy Chen","email":"tommy351@gmail.com","url":"http://zespia.tw"},"description":"Front-matter parser.","dist-tags":{"latest":"5.0.0"},"license":"MIT","maintainers":[{"name":"jlhwung","email":"jlhwung@gmail.com"},{"name":"hexobot","email":"hexojs@gmail.com"},{"name":"tommy351","email":"tommy351@gmail.com"},{"name":"tomap","email":"piartt@gmail.com"},{"name":"abnerchou","email":"hi@abnerchou.me"},{"name":"curben","email":"bushedge@protonmail.com"},{"name":"ertrzyiks","email":"mateusz.derks@gmail.com"},{"name":"yoshinorin","email":"yoshinorin.net@outlook.com"}],"name":"hexo-front-matter","readme":"# hexo-front-matter\n\n[![CI](https://github.com/hexojs/hexo-front-matter/actions/workflows/ci.yml/badge.svg?branch=master)](https://github.com/hexojs/hexo-front-matter/actions/workflows/ci.yml)\n[![NPM version](https://badge.fury.io/js/hexo-front-matter.svg)](https://www.npmjs.com/package/hexo-front-matter)\n[![Coverage Status](https://coveralls.io/repos/github/hexojs/hexo-front-matter/badge.svg)](https://coveralls.io/github/hexojs/hexo-front-matter)\n\nFront-matter parser.\n\n## What is Front-matter?\n\nFront-matter allows you to specify data at the top of a file. Here are two formats:\n\n**YAML front-matter**\n\n```\n---\nlayout: false\ntitle: \"Hello world\"\n---\nLorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.\n```\n\n**JSON front-matter**\n\n```\n;;;\n\"layout\": false,\n\"title\": \"Hello world\"\n;;;\nLorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.\n```\n\nPrefixing separators are optional.\n\n## API\n\n### parse(str, [options])\n\nParses front-matter.\n\n### stringify(obj, [options])\n\nConverts an object to a front-matter string.\n\nOption | Description | Default\n--- | --- | ---\n`mode` | The mode can be either `json` or `yaml`. | `yaml`\n`separator` | Separator | `---`\n`prefixSeparator` | Add prefixing separator. | `false`\n\n### split(str)\n\nSplits a YAML front-matter string.\n\n### escape(str)\n\nConverts hard tabs to soft tabs.\n\n## License\n\nMIT","time":{"created":"2022-01-26T21:59:18.746Z","modified":"2025-12-03T09:45:31.089Z","2.0.0":"2020-07-25T06:32:33.497Z","1.0.0":"2019-08-30T08:24:10.500Z","0.2.3":"2016-06-13T12:28:17.252Z","0.2.2":"2015-02-11T06:47:57.605Z","0.2.1":"2015-01-23T16:40:47.422Z","0.2.0":"2015-01-23T16:15:24.644Z","0.1.0":"2015-01-07T08:52:55.742Z","0.0.4":"2014-07-23T08:36:31.001Z","0.0.3":"2014-07-13T07:29:37.187Z","0.0.2":"2014-07-03T16:25:37.513Z","0.0.1":"2014-07-03T15:53:54.226Z","3.0.0":"2022-01-03T01:18:52.689Z","4.0.0":"2022-10-25T14:04:27.901Z","4.1.0":"2023-04-20T13:46:14.413Z","4.2.0":"2023-10-31T08:49:56.856Z","4.2.1":"2023-10-31T12:06:09.704Z","5.0.0":"2025-11-04T14:46:50.636Z"},"versions":{"2.0.0":{"name":"hexo-front-matter","version":"2.0.0","description":"Front-matter parser.","main":"lib/front_matter","scripts":{"eslint":"eslint .","test":"mocha test/index.js","test-cov":"nyc npm run test"},"directories":{"lib":"./lib"},"repository":{"type":"git","url":"git+https://github.com/hexojs/hexo-front-matter.git"},"keywords":["front-matter","front matter","yaml","yml","hexo","json"],"author":{"name":"Tommy Chen","email":"tommy351@gmail.com","url":"http://zespia.tw"},"license":"MIT","dependencies":{"js-yaml":"^3.13.1"},"devDependencies":{"chai":"^4.2.0","eslint":"^7.1.0","eslint-config-hexo":"^4.0.0","mocha":"^8.0.1","moment":"^2.24.0","nyc":"^15.0.0"},"engines":{"node":">=10.13.0"},"gitHead":"ccbdff36d151a56932418cdc6d0329d866032a1b","bugs":{"url":"https://github.com/hexojs/hexo-front-matter/issues"},"homepage":"https://github.com/hexojs/hexo-front-matter#readme","_id":"hexo-front-matter@2.0.0","_nodeVersion":"14.4.0","_npmVersion":"6.14.5","dist":{"shasum":"03f39a9eedb16c5448dbb3bec7dff2c4e224006c","size":2347,"noattachment":false,"tarball":"https://registry.npmmirror.com/hexo-front-matter/-/hexo-front-matter-2.0.0.tgz","integrity":"sha512-IR3tjAyK2Ga/0a/WDAoNy5+n3j